olspan="2"><div align="right">        <p align="left">田中先生はビデオを見せてくださいました。Mr. Tanaka showed us a video (Tanaka is doing          it for us).<br>          本田さんは私<span class="style2">の</span>へやをそうじをしてくれました。Honda cleaned my room (for me).<span class="style2"><span class="style3"><br>          </span></span></p>        </div></td>  </tr></table><p>&nbsp;</p><table width="90%" border="1" align="center">  <tr>    <td width="48%" height="19" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><div align="left"><br>いただく、もらう<br>    </div></td>    <td width="52%" bgcolor="#cccccc"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="37"><p align="right"> Te-f. of verb + いただく、もらう</p></td>    <td height="37">I had someone do something for me </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="68" colspan="2"><div align="right">        <p align="left">田中先生に日本語を教えていただきました。I had Mr. Tanaka teach me Japanese.          (Tanaka is doing it for me).<br>          本田さんに私<span class="style2">の</span>へやをそうじをしてもらいました。I had Honda-san          clean my room (for me).<span class="style2"><span class="style3"><br>          </span></span></p>        </div></td>  </tr></table><p>&nbsp;</p><UL><LI><a href="GiveReceive_2.pdf">Giving and Receiving (favor): illustration (pdf)</a><BR><BR></LI>	<LI>Giving and Receiving			<B>練習 (Practice Quizzes)</B>			<ul>			  <li>Quiz: <a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412k/gq_y2_412k_GR_action.php">G/R Action: doing something as a favor to someone</a></li>			</ul>	</LI></LI> 			 			<p align="center"><a href="#top">Return to Top</a> </p> 			<p align="center"><a href="../../../../glist.php">Ｒeturn to Grammar Lists</a></p>	  </UL>          </tr></table></BODY></HTML>